  "system": {
    "biography": {
      "value": "<p>A Whispervane is a messenger and a mild nuisance. It has no meaningful combat presence. A summoner who calls one for a fight has misread what they summoned. Called to deliver a message without being seen, locate a specific sound within a building, or harass an archer's concentration, it performs reliably. Its intelligence is sufficient to understand a destination and a recipient — not sufficient to improvise if circumstances change.</p>"
